data.description: BRING YOUR POOL TABLE & GIANT TV!!!  H U G E  Gameroom keeps the action going in this SOLID Home!!! Solid block construction. BIG privacy fenced backyard, plenty of room for pool, trampoline, swing set & BBQ. This home was completely redone less than 2 years ago. NEW roof, NEW windows, NEW countertops, NEW HVAC (heat & air), NEW paint, NEW flooring etc. Very sensible floor plan that flows GREAT! Good size master bedroom with walk in closet! County owns the green belt across the street, so quiet, peaceful & WONDERFUL! You will have the BEST Super bowl around in the Huge Gameroom!!!
